Package: risenricher
Title: Enrich Scholarly References Using Open APIs
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Santiago Ortega", "Ed",  role = c("co-aut", "co-cre"))
Description: Batch enrichment and harmonization of scholarly references
    using multiple open scholarly APIs. Supports candidate scoring,
    field-level provenance, caching, and optional Python fallback.
